            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"the-latency-you-are-hiding\">The latency you are hiding</h3>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The reason occupancy matters: the memory hierarchy spans <strong>nearly three orders\nof magnitude</strong> in latency. A kernel that stalls on DRAM without enough other work\nin flight is throwing away the chip. The bar chart below (log scale) is the\nsingle most important picture in the course.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
